{"tid":2409848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅興亞人勢力代表　促請軍方釋放 昂山素姬 等民盟領袖","createTime":"2021-02-16T06:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T07:08:40.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"35b839aaefd47dee4ca03078532f053a22e8af59","tid":2409848,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158804820615491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbencrox%2Fposts%2F10158804820615491&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=6d7a7b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158804820615491</a><br />\n<br />\nTed Lin:<br />\n黃/紅色不是主色調，黑色才是CDM主色<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3898488170236774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3898488170236774&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=e91ecbc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3898488170236774</a><br />\n<br />\n有示威者呼籲，國民參與「公民抗命運動」（civil disobedience movement, CDM），反對軍事政變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158804820615491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbencrox%2Fposts%2F10158804820615491&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=6d7a7b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158804820615491</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Ben Crox<br />\n<br />\n由於民盟執政並不是那麼令人滿意，又或者說，示威者並不一定希望被歸類為民盟的死忠，而是為了全緬所有人而站出來，所以由邊區（比較不支持民盟 / 88 世代的）開始，越來越多人選擇穿上黑色服裝，既代表「少數、被忽略、邊沿、貧苦」的意思，也為軍閥僭政的前景暗黑表達哀傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158780842210491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbencrox%2Fposts%2F10158780842210491&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=82740a15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158780842210491</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Ben Crox<br />\n<br />\n被指不滿民盟不點地方票的「羅興亞人地域」，勢力代表也在促請軍方釋放昂山素姬等民盟領袖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhttps://hk. appledaily. com/international/20210210/H5WUIRAYPJHGXLDJUDTQ7237OQ/<br />\n<br />\n羅興亞維權分子韋韋努坦言擔心在目前政局拉鋸狀態下，軍方會在邊境興兵鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n雖然昂山素姬也敵視羅興亞人，但韋韋努還是希望對方可以獲釋，並恢復領導民選政府，她又認為目前反對派的抗爭運動，將會為緬甸注入新的希望，事關「帶領抗爭的新一代抱有進步觀點，談論民主時會比較包容」。<br />\n<br />\n另一名羅興亞維權人士欽蒙也有類似的看法，呼籲外界抵制緬甸的「改革」把戲，認清敏昂萊才是迫害少數民族的主要元兇。"},{"pid":"559ef967a8bcd8b69d39b8e086778ab3070b948f","tid":2409848,"uid":232370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"又係一條左膠"},{"pid":"408cd0d9f77bf3354a576a673b42e19b3ee54b86","tid":2409848,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"咩光環都攞晒"},{"pid":"31bba8ec7ad8914182ec72e5bd472ca92d54f40f","tid":2409848,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:53:11.000Z","msg":"緬甸版社民連<br />\n<br />\n睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189f318b4c92e67194b9719795b47633fbe89bff","tid":2409848,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"連羅興亞人都出嚟抽水"}]}